{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bebc524a05","title":"给谢觉截的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"afddef3b8d","index":0,"year":1942,"month":8,"day":15,"articleId":"bebc524a05"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji17.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji17":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"55c9364270","type":"paragraph","text":"给谢觉截的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"bebc524a05"},{"id":"514eb3a280","type":"paragraph","text":"（1942年8月15日）关于“还政于民”这个口号之不要，我记得对你说过了。早几天解放报社论末带有“官方干部”“纯老百姓代表”的话，也有不要处，不知此文是否你写的？我们的政府是真正代表老百姓的，是民的，故不可说“还政于民”，也不可分为“官方”“非官方”。那天社论的意思并不坏，是说要让新选代表多说话，只是不宜将“官方”“纯老百姓”这样对称起来。请加考虑。1这是毛泽东致谢觉截信的主要内容。谢觉数，当时任中共中央西北局副书记、陕昔宁边区参议会副议长。[2]指1942年8月12日《解放日报》社论《迎接第二届第二次遗区参","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"bebc524a05"}],"page":{"id":"d5ddd30ce5","publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"bebc524a05","start":118,"end":118}}}},"__N_SSG":true}